                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Nise/">Nise</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-03-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读过</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="445145259">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-445145259" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-445145259" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="445145259">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/etymon/">連山</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-10-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">章句論大佳，古籍整理者宜詳看。字例略說中談漢字與洋字部份，呂說有未達者。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

